        <div class='panel-heading'>
          <h3 class='panel-title'>Our Project</h3>
        </div>
        <div class='panel-body'>We have decided that we want our wedding to make a difference in the world so have decided to sponsor the following project as our wedding registry.  Below you will see a list of items that this project requires to get off the ground and we invite you to choose the items that you would like to purchase on our behalf.
        </div>
      </div>
		</div>
	</div>
	
	<div class='row featurette'>
    <div class='col-md-4'>
      <img class='featurette-image user-project-img' src='<%= @project.project_pic %>'>
    </div>
    <div class='col-md-8'>
      <h2 class='featurette-heading'><%= @project.project_name %></h2>
      <h3><%= @project.project_location %></h3>
      <h3><%= @project.project_type %></h3>
      <h3>$<%= @project.project_amount %></h3>
      <p ><%= @project.project_description %></p>

    </div>
  </div>


